topic.title: Tech CEO's testifying before congress.
topic.body: CEO's of giant monopolies are trying to explain how they are not committing anti-trust violations. Hopefully something comes out of this but I'm not holding my breath.

topic.title: Zeronet is opening as a new user?
topic.body: When I opened zeronet today all my sites were gone and it showed the new user greeting. I checked my zeronet folder and all of my files are still there and when I reconnect to 08chan the files I had load immediately and it showed up in my favorites list. Has anyone else had this problem?
